{"tid":727830,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"贊奴沙：訓練果陣 比人大大力踢傷！！！","createTime":"2018-07-03T10:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T10:30:46.000Z","uid":10338,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5c77e07939f6fd95827b7f3bdb2497e8ef468e7f","tid":727830,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"比利時和日本的淘汰賽后，記者在混合區見到了贊奴沙。他的膝蓋被層層包裹著，好在傷勢沒有看上去的那麼嚴重。<br />\n&ldquo;休息三四天就夠了。&rdquo;贊奴沙說道：&ldquo;我在訓練時被重重踢了一腳，有時候這就會發生。我一開始以為什麼東西斷了，但好在最後發現沒事。對巴西的比賽時我肯定可以恢復的。&rdquo;<br />\n談到對日本的比賽，贊奴沙說道：&ldquo;是的，我在後備席上很擔心。但當我們打進扳平的進球時，我100%知道我們會逆轉了。現在我們可以帶著自信面對巴西。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"0cd96402182c822e7c81cb629eb690432324da43","tid":727830,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"抵啦，做英雄入波拎首名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dca093a63df215f2ac65359d23fdf9fab77179d","tid":727830,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"逞強狗"},{"pid":"864b3c894faeada90f62d3b26607034c98a617a7","tid":727830,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"對巴西的比賽時我肯定可以恢復的<br />\n<br />\n隊友: 本來唔洗對巴西架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be30bff6e6ee1c3057755c06e95c5b6cb9f9cb3a","tid":727830,"uid":4444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"對巴西都冇你份啦柒頭"},{"pid":"0e204919d7dfe08785b34e1ddcf593e118ca50ed","tid":727830,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:26:53.000Z","msg":"本來穩入四強 你條仆街"},{"pid":"4fddaa8450afc4eebb7c3fd50b133e1e97af8882","tid":727830,"uid":55923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03